  <summary date="2022-08-11T13:18:07Z" status="Introduced in House">Safe Travel Act

This bill requires proof of COVID-19 vaccinations or proof of negative COVID-19 test results for passengers on planes and Amtrak trains; patrons of airports; and employees, contractors, and subcontractors of air carriers, airports, and Amtrak.</summary>
